keyFacts: Jeffrey Epstein traveled extensively via private aircraft between July 2017 and April 2019, with over 80 recorded entries/exits in this log.

Epstein used at least three different passport/document numbers (566672615, 469911707, 547017616) during this period.
The flights used multiple private aircraft tail numbers, including N212JE, N120JE, and N415LM.
